{"text_id":201460,"tokens":["Crystal"," Diamond"," is"," a"," term"," used"," in"," ge","mology"," to"," refer"," to"," a"," diamond"," that"," has"," undergone"," a"," specific"," process"," to"," enhance"," its"," clarity"," and"," brilliance","."," This"," process"," involves"," the"," use"," of"," high"," temperatures"," and"," pressures"," to"," mimic"," the"," natural"," conditions"," under"," which"," diamonds"," are"," formed","."," The"," result"," is"," a"," diamond"," that"," is"," virtually"," indistingu","ishable"," from"," a"," naturally"," occurring"," one"," in"," terms"," of"," its"," physical"," properties"," and"," appearance","."," The"," process"," of"," creating"," a"," crystal"," diamond"," begins"," with"," a"," rough"," diamond",","," which"," is"," subjected"," to"," high"," temperatures"," and"," pressures"," in"," a"," controlled"," environment","."," This"," process",","," known"," as"," High"," Temperature"," High"," Pressure"," (","HTH","P",")"," treatment",","," can"," significantly"," improve"," the"," clarity"," of"," the"," diamond"," by"," removing"," or"," reducing"," the"," visibility"," of"," inclusions"," and"," blemishes","."," The"," result"," is"," a"," diamond"," that"," has"," the"," same"," hardness",","," refractive"," index",","," and"," dispersion"," as"," a"," natural"," diamond",","," but"," with"," enhanced"," clarity"," and"," brilliance","."," Crystal"," diamonds"," are"," not"," to"," be"," confused"," with"," synthetic"," or"," lab","-","grown"," diamonds",","," which"," are"," created"," from"," carbon"," under"," high"," pressure"," and"," high"," temperature"," conditions","."," While"," synthetic"," diamonds"," also"," have"," the"," same"," physical"," properties"," as"," natural"," diamonds",","," they"," are"," created"," from"," scratch"," in"," a"," laboratory",","," whereas"," crystal"," diamonds"," are"," natural"," diamonds"," that"," have"," been"," treated"," to"," improve"," their"," clarity","."," The"," use"," of"," crystal"," diamonds"," in"," jewelry"," has"," been"," a"," subject"," of"," debate"," within"," the"," ge","mo","logical"," community","."," Some"," argue"," that"," the"," treatment"," process"," is"," a"," form"," of"," enhancement"," that"," should"," be"," disclosed"," to"," consumers",","," while"," others"," believe"," that"," since"," the"," process"," does"," not"," alter"," the"," inherent"," properties"," of"," the"," diamond",","," it"," should"," not"," be"," considered"," a"," treatment","."," Despite"," the"," controversy",","," crystal"," diamonds"," have"," gained"," popularity"," in"," recent"," years"," due"," to"," their"," affordability"," and"," the"," fact"," that"," they"," offer"," a"," viable"," alternative"," to"," more"," expensive",","," naturally"," occurring"," diamonds","."," They"," are"," particularly"," popular"," in"," engagement"," rings"," and"," other"," high","-","end"," jewelry"," pieces","."," In"," conclusion",","," a"," crystal"," diamond"," is"," a"," natural"," diamond"," that"," has"," undergone"," a"," specific"," treatment"," process"," to"," enhance"," its"," clarity"," and"," brilliance","."," Despite"," some"," controversy"," within"," the"," ge","mo","logical"," community",","," these"," diamonds"," have"," gained"," popularity"," due"," to"," their"," affordability"," and"," the"," fact"," that"," they"," offer"," a"," viable"," alternative"," to"," naturally"," occurring"," diamonds","."],"sub_source":"wikipedia","model":"gpt4","label":1}